                        <interp inst="t18641024-1013-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.—<hi rend="italic">They were both further charged with having been before convicted, M'Carthy at Winchester in July</hi>, 1860, <hi rend="italic">and Chassion at this Court in January</hi>, 1862; <hi rend="italic">to which they both</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
